{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047440/extras/Maple_Leaf.png?t=1733030388\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>A Beaver's Tale</strong></i> is a Canadian-made game by a solo developer, offering a short, story-driven experience designed to be completed in about 30 minutes. For those seeking extended play and creativity, it features an optional build mode. It's the perfect choice for players looking for a concise and enjoyable experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047440/extras/steam-front-page.png?t=1733030388\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GET TO THE NEXT ISLAND BY BUILDING DAMS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <u><strong>Story Mode</strong></u>, you play as <strong><i>Buckey the Beaver</i></strong>. You can go swimming in the river, munch down some trees, and build dams with logs. Drama strikes when one of your kits gets stuck on a neighboring island, and you need to build your way across. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047440/extras/ezgif-4-34291404fe.gif?t=1733030388\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your Goose neighbour, <strong><i>Cecilothy</i></strong>, does <i>not</i> like your beaver kits running all over the place. He\u2019s got a mean streak as long as his beak, so you\u2019d be better off staying out of his feathers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUILD A HOME FOR YOUR FAMILY AND BECOME A MASTER BEAVER BUILDER ALONG THE WAY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Despite the bright colors, A Beaver's Tale is a story about loss, grief and parenthood in the wild. Building a home for your 